Below Deck - Season 2, Episode 7




She'd Better Not Be Staying

The Ohana crew is very unhappy to learn Adrienne will be coming onboard as a guest, and when she blows the lid off the lingering tension between Kat and Amy, the boat erupts in total chaos. Kelley and Jennice's awkward tension is becoming noticeable to their crewmates, and Amy feels isolated when Kat and Kate turn against her.
